---
// Grid de casos de estudio con foco en problemas, proceso y resultados
---

<section id="proyectos" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Featured Projects</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">From concept to deployment: how I build applications, teach technology, and deliver measurable results.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Case 1 -->
      <article class="card overflow-hidden group">
        <img src="/avatar.png" alt="iOS Application" class="h-52 w-full object-cover group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300" />
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="tag">Swift</span>
            <span class="tag">iOS</span>
            <span class="tag">REST API</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Native iOS Application Development</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 text-sm">Built optimized native interfaces for multiple Apple devices with REST API integration and improved performance through technical analysis.</p>
          <a href="#" class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center text-slate-900 font-medium">View project →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Case 2 -->
      <article class="card overflow-hidden group">
        <img src="/avatar.png" alt="Educational Robotics" class="h-52 w-full object-cover group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300" />
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="tag">Education</span>
            <span class="tag">Scratch</span>
            <span class="tag">Robotics</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Educational Robotics Program</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 text-sm">Designed progressive learning plans for 55+ students achieving 80% project completion rate through hands-on challenges and collaborative dynamics.</p>
          <a href="#" class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center text-slate-900 font-medium">View program →</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
